    • javafx.application.Application

  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AppSnakeFX

    public abstract class BaseApplication
extends javafx.application.Application
    Author:
    Benjamin Wulfert The baseApplication is the parent class for the snakefx-client. Its the configuration class for the client and holds references to the stompClient, the UserConfig, etc.
